3864static inline void hpm_ffa_cfft_q15(q15_t *src, uint32_t m)
3865{
3866 fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
3867 xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
3868 xfer.src = src;
3869 xfer.dst = src;
3870 xfer.is_ifft = false;
3871 xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
3872 xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
3873 ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
3874}
3883static inline void hpm_ffa_cfft_q31(q31_t *src, uint32_t m)
3884{
3885 fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
3886 xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
3887 xfer.src = src;
3888 xfer.dst = src;
3889 xfer.is_ifft = false;
3890 xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q31;
3891 xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q31;
3892 ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
3893}
3902static inline void hpm_ffa_cifft_q15(q15_t *src, uint32_t m)
3903{
3904 fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
3905 xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
3906 xfer.src = src;
3907 xfer.dst = src;
3908 xfer.is_ifft = true;
3909 xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
3910 xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q15;
3911 ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
3912}
3913
3922static inline void hpm_ffa_cifft_q31(q31_t *src, uint32_t m)
3923{
3924 fft_xfer_t xfer = { 0 };
3925 xfer.num_points = 1 << m;
3926 xfer.src = src;
3927 xfer.dst = src;
3928 xfer.is_ifft = true;
3929 xfer.src_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q31;
3930 xfer.dst_data_type = FFA_DATA_TYPE_COMPLEX_Q31;
3931 ffa_calculate_fft_blocking(HPM_FFA, &xfer);
3932}
